 />\n巴打請TG: shelll<br />\n因為我兩個加你三個就perfect池"},{"pid":"ff0529e9aaf6a31323671dccf1be6dd7e51157ed","tid":140341,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"其實都想去埋林芝<br />\n手頭上都有司機聯絡方法<br />\n但由於兩個人包車無咁抵<br />\n想睇下有無巴絲都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8f5e5d235ba54a07d6453f79f67a01c5452ba1","tid":140341,"uid":88185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"你地係唔係已經夠人數啦？"},{"pid":"576f6021fbd39e36e13a316c3372659b94431223","tid":140341,"uid":103034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"我同朋友兩個女仔都係五月去，你地拼哂未?"},{"pid":"403c2db9d6fca0b4fedaef0c15fd082381333ace","tid":140341,"uid":103034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地係唔係已經夠人數啦？</blockquote><br />\n Halo我都係想拼車<br />\n兩個女仔<br />\n有興趣留tg俾我或者add我tg傾丫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntg: reyjkvik"},{"pid":"71e5c1eda9e41920154b46683f0a439bddc31bd2","tid":140341,"uid":33387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都想去埋林芝<br />\n手頭上都有司機聯絡方法<br />\n但由於兩個人包車無咁抵<br />\n想睇下有無巴絲都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得林芝都幾伏下 同埋其實可以去到青旅先再搵人拼車"},{"pid":"b38eb4fd7f1d4e0c779a6216c60fdd430d890966","tid":140341,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:50:42.000Z","msg":"唔該哂各位巴絲 暫時齊腳了<br />\n不過5月7打後去到12號就可能到時報local tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}